--- src/compress.js ---
@sig d51f1fb0
estimateTokens()→Math.ceil|estimates token count from str length
extractLegend()→basename,lines.push,parse,Math.max,source.slice,beforeNode.match|parses AST to extract exports & JSDocs into compact legend string
export compressFile()→extname,SUPPORTED_EXTENSIONS.has,readFileSync,estimateTokens,source.trim,minify|minifies JS/TS via Terser, prepends JSDoc legend
PATTERNS: AST traversal|regex JSDoc extraction|Terser minification
EDGE_CASES: empty file→empty code|parse err→fallback to regex strip
